from transferring Colonel Cochrane.

36:22.400 --> 36:23.760
One thing's for sure -

36:23.760 --> 36:26.960
NASA won't be sending the Colonel
on another mission.

36:26.960 --> 36:29.680
I think he's returned from
    space a born-again mess.

36:29.680 --> 36:33.440
I don't understand why his spiritual
awakening should disqualify him.

36:33.440 --> 36:37.040
He's shouting from the mountain top
about walking with God.

