here, his doctor agrees with him.

37:05.080 --> 37:06.240
       For whatever reason.

37:06.240 --> 37:08.360
That should be the end
of the discussion.

37:08.360 --> 37:10.480
I know, in a normal circumstance,
you'd respect that.

37:10.480 --> 37:12.200
