before patient care.

37:12.200 --> 37:14.480
I listened to what
the Colonel had to say!

37:14.480 --> 37:18.040
          Did you really?

37:18.040 --> 37:20.120
Knowing you was supposed
to make this easier -

37:20.120 --> 37:21.280
that's why they sent me.

37:21.280 --> 37:24.640
