37:51.720 --> 37:55.720
Then why is it
you know so little about people?

38:01.720 --> 38:05.720
Well, I guess this means we
won't be sleeping together tonight.

38:07.040 --> 38:11.040
It's been great
    seeing you again, Donald.

38:15.760 --> 38:19.760
