40:53.960 --> 40:55.360
Where are your sons now?

40:55.360 --> 40:59.360
Les is with Hewlett-Packard.
Good with computers.

40:59.760 --> 41:03.760
And Gene Junior, he's a civil
engineer down in Connecticut.

41:04.680 --> 41:06.480
You should be proud.

41:06.480 --> 41:08.400
They're good boys.

41:08.400 --> 41:11.040
I meant of yourself.

41:11.040 --> 41:15.040
Barbara's bottle must be ready now.

41:16.560 --> 41:20.040
Mark, I want to thank you
for what you're doing for Vonnie.

41:20.040 --> 41:22.480
I watched you at the hospital today.

41:22.480 --> 41:24.840
You treat her as if
    she were one of your own.

41:24.840 --> 41:26.560
She's a part of my family.

41:26.560 --> 41:30.120
About what you said about Steve...

41:30.120 --> 41:31.920
Stephen came to trust you.

41:31.920 --> 41:35.600
